{
  "chapter": 26,
  "chapter_summary": "本章中，马如龙在杂货店继续试探张老实，怀疑他与大婉和隐藏高手身份有关。孙早、孙迟这对天生畸形的孪生兄弟入店挑战，表面坦率自尊，实则趁马如龙放下敌意时施下无形毒。张老实用花生断杖、隔空封穴，并取药救醒马如龙，暴露出深不可测的内家功力。马如龙仍坚持放走孙氏兄弟，随后追问大婉下落。谢玉宝因嫉妒与痛苦揭露大婉只是自己的丫头，而马如龙坦言不论身份美丑仍会想念她。与此同时，二十八名黑衣人进入陋巷，杂货店外局势骤变。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "大婉。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "大碗？你要大碗？碗都在厨房里，你是不是要我去拿给你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "我说的大婉是一个人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你没有见过她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_sun_zao",
      "text": "两位来买什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_zao",
      "speaker_name": "孙早",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们什么都不买。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chi",
      "speaker_name": "孙迟",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们只不过想来看看，你究竟是个什么样的人，居然能把王万武留住，是用什么法子留住的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_zao",
      "speaker_name": "孙早",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我姓孙，名孙早，",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chi",
      "speaker_name": "孙迟",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为我出世时比他迟了一点。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_zao",
      "speaker_name": "孙早",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们是孪生人，又天生畸形，这种人通常都喜欢冒称为星宿门下。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chi",
      "speaker_name": "孙迟",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "所以你一定也认为我们是星宿海门下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_zao",
      "speaker_name": "孙早",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "但是你错了，我们和星宿海别无关系。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chi",
      "speaker_name": "孙迟",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "十年前我们曾经到星宿海走过一次，我们也想找到传说中的异人，传给我们一点能够无敌于天下的绝艺。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_zao",
      "speaker_name": "孙早",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可惜我们失望了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chi",
      "speaker_name": "孙迟",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那里只不过是一片荒无人烟的穷荒之地，夏日酷热，冬日苦寒，任何人都很难生存。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_zao",
      "speaker_name": "孙早",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们告诉你这些事，只不过要你知道，我们的武功，都是我们自己苦练出来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chi",
      "speaker_name": "孙迟",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "所以你如果也想留下我们，不必有任何顾忌。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_sun_zao",
      "text": "我不想留下你们。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_sun_zao",
      "text": "你们随时都可以走。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_zao",
      "speaker_name": "孙早",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们也看得出你没有把我们当作仇敌，如果你是别人，我们说不定会结个朋友。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_chi",
      "speaker_name": "孙迟",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你实在不是个奸险的小人，只可惜你是马如龙。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你想干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我想留下他们。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不想，我想。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在你是不是已经知道我为什么要留下他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "放他们走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "现在就放他们走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "因为我是马如龙，因为他们做的只不过是他们自觉应该做的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你真的没有见过大婉，也不知道她是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你一直都只是这家杂货店的伙计？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "该问的事他不问，该问的人他也不去问，却偏偏来问我这些废话。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "我知道我应该去问王万武，这次他们究竟来了多少人？来的都是些什么人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你为什么不去问？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "因为我现在问的这件事更重要。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "重要，有什么重要？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我见过大婉又如何？没见过大婉又如何？你为什么一定要问？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "因为我想知道她在哪里？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "我一定要知道。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她在哪里，跟你又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "当然有关系。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "如果你也曾想念过一个人，你就会明白的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你想知道大婉的事，为什么不进来问我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你认得大婉？这件事就是你们两个串通好来害我的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你一直都在想念她？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你天天跟我在一起，可是你天天都想念她？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你为什么要想念她？难道你喜欢那个丑八怪？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你想不想知道她是谁？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我想。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "如果你知道她谁，说不定会很失望的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我不会，绝不会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "不管她是谁都一样。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "好，我告诉你，",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她只不过是我的一个丫头而已。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你是大小姐，她是丫头，你是美人，她是丑八怪，不管你是什么人，她是什么人，我还是一样可以想念她。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你回来，我还有话告诉你。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "我是个好色的人，我一辈子，最少已经有过几百个女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "我也差不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "但是我始终不了解女人，",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "我这一辈子都无法了解。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "我也是一样。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    }
  ],
